  "keyFeatures": [
    "Modular flake-parts composition with explicit host, user, system profile, and home profile selectors",
    "Multi-platform support: NixOS (x86_64 + ARM), nix-darwin (Apple Silicon), and standalone Home Manager",
    "Layered system and home profiles (tty, sway, sway-full) for capability-oriented configuration",
    "Shared my.* options namespace for repo-local values flowing across NixOS and Home Manager modules",
    "AI tooling overlay with claude-code, qwen-code, codex, opencode, and ollama",
    "Sway desktop with Waybar, swaylock, fuzzel, mako, and theming support",
    "Self-hosted Soft Serve git server on boreal with SSH and HTTP interfaces",
    "Jellyfin media server with declarative path and ACL management via my.jellyfin.* options",
    "Podman-first container runtime with Quadlet, compose, and npm app scaffolding",
    "Rich Nix helper surface (nr, nrb, ncopy, nboh) for local and remote deployment workflows"
  ],
